程序包 org.janusgraph.diskstorage.util

类 MetricInstrumentedSlicesIterator

java.lang.Object
org.janusgraph.diskstorage.util.MetricInstrumentedSlicesIterator
所有已实现的接口:
Closeable, AutoCloseable, Iterator<StaticBuffer>, KeySlicesIterator, RecordIterator<StaticBuffer>
public class MetricInstrumentedSlicesIterator
extends Object
implements KeySlicesIterator
This class is used by MetricInstrumentedStore to measure wall clock time, method invocation counts, and exceptions thrown by the methods on RecordIterator instances returned from MetricInstrumentedStore.getSlice(org.janusgraph.diskstorage.keycolumnvalue.KeySliceQuery, org.janusgraph.diskstorage.keycolumnvalue.StoreTransaction).
作者:
Dan LaRocque (dalaro@hopcount.org)

    • of

      public static MetricInstrumentedSlicesIterator of​(KeySlicesIterator keyIterator, String... prefix)
      If the iterator argument is non-null, then return a new MetricInstrumentedIterator wrapping it. Metrics for method calls on the wrapped instance will be prefixed with the string prefix which must be non-null. If the iterator argument is null, then return null.
      参数:
      keyIterator - the iterator to wrap with Metrics measurements
      prefix - the Metrics name prefix string
      返回:
      a wrapper around keyIterator or null if keyIterator is null

    • getEntries

      public Map<SliceQuery,​RecordIterator<Entry>> getEntries()
      从接口复制的说明: KeySlicesIterator
      Returns map of iterators over all entries associated with the current key that match the column range specified in the queries.

      Closing any of the returned sub-iterators has no effect on this iterator. Calling Iterator.next() might close previously returned RecordIterators depending on the implementation, hence it is important to iterate over (and close) the RecordIterator before calling Iterator.next() or Iterator.hasNext(). Important! Entries should be sorted inside iterators. Otherwise VertexJobConverter will not work correctly
